structure.unit: JUVENILE PROCEEDINGS -- COMMITMENT AND CARE OF CHILDREN

law.history: Repealed 1986 Ky. Acts ch. 423, sec. 198, effective July 1, 1987. -- Amended 1978 Ky. Acts ch. 66, sec. 3, effective June 17, 1978. -- Amended 1976 Ky. Acts ch. 406, sec. 309, effective January 1, 1975. -- Amended 1974 Ky. Acts ch. 406, sec. 309, effective January 1, 1975. -- Amended 1972 Ky. Acts ch. 239, sec. 1, para. (7), effective June 16, 1972. -- Amended 1964 Ky. Acts ch. 85, sec. 4, effective June 18, 1964. -- Amended 1962 Ky. Acts ch. 212, sec. 11, effective June 14, 1962. -- Created 1952 Ky. Acts ch. 161, sec. 60, effective January 1, 1953. Note: This section was repealed by 1980 Ky. Acts ch. 280, which was to have become effective July 1, 1982. Thereafter, 1982 Ky. Acts ch. 284 changed the effective date of that act to July 15, 1984. Then, 1984 Ky. Acts ch. 184 repealed both 1980 Ky. Acts ch. 280, and 1982 Ky. Acts ch. 284.
